twitter:title: Politics and Policy in New York Real Estate
twitter:description: The Hudson Gateway Association of Realtors and OneKey® MLS hosted a virtual panel featuring experts who surveyed New York’s political landscape, looked at laws and regulations, and shared intel on what real estate professionals need to know to support the industry.
